Minsheng Halts Loans for Second-Home Buyers, Shanghai Daily Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-04-14T19:47:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/minsheng-halts-loans-for-second-home-buyers-shanghai-daily-says.html
China Minsheng Banking Corp. has
stopped mortgage services for second-home buyers and has
lengthened the approval procedure for loans on first homes,
Shanghai Daily said, citing unidentified people.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  